5
00:01:56,319 --> 00:01:57,952
- AHH.

6
00:01:59,252 --> 00:02:01,152
- YOU SURE YOU DIDN'T
FORGET ANYTHING?

7
00:02:01,185 --> 00:02:02,419
- I DON'T GET
TO GO BACK VERY OFTEN,

8
00:02:02,452 --> 00:02:06,285
