10
00:02:07,352 --> 00:02:09,252
- YES! DRIED POTATOES.

11
00:02:09,285 --> 00:02:10,519
- AND FOR SHIPPO.

12
00:02:10,552 --> 00:02:11,585
HERE YOU GO!

13
00:02:11,619 --> 00:02:14,419
- WOW! THANK YOU, KAGOME!

14
00:02:15,252 --> 00:02:17,352
THIS IS YUMMY.

15
00:02:18,019 --> 00:02:18,819
AAH!

16
00:02:18,852 --> 00:02:21,752
OH, LOOK, IT'S SPINNING
ALL BY ITSELF!

17
00:02:22,319 --> 00:02:23,985
- HERE YOU GO, MIROKU.

18
00:02:24,019 --> 00:02:26,085
- ACCEPTED WITH PLEASURE.

19
00:02:27,885 --> 00:02:28,819
- WHERE'S SANGO?

20
00:02:28,852 --> 00:02:30,419
- SHE HASN'T COME BACK
FROM HER VILLAGE YET.

21
00:02:30,452 --> 00:02:32,319
[CRUNCHING]

22
00:02:32,352 --> 00:02:33,419
- IT'S BEEN DAYS,

23
00:02:33,452 --> 00:02:35,052
SO I THOUGHT FOR SURE
SHE WOULD HAVE COME BACK BY NOW.

24
00:02:35,085 --> 00:02:37,852
- SHE HASN'T BEEN
TO HER VILLAGE IN A WHILE.

25
00:02:37,885 --> 00:02:39,619
SHE PROBABLY HAD LOTS TO DO.

26
00:02:39,652 --> 00:02:42,185
YOU KNOW,
BESIDES REPAIRING HER WEAPON.

27
00:02:42,219 --> 00:02:44,552
- MAYBE SHE'S NOT
GONNA COME BACK

28
00:02:44,585 --> 00:02:47,885
BECAUSE OF A CERTAIN LECHER
WHO WON'T LEAVE HER ALONE.

29
00:02:47,919 --> 00:02:50,885
- I AM GUILTY OF NO SUCH THING!

30
00:02:50,919 --> 00:02:52,085
- SURE, WHATEVER.

31
00:02:52,119 --> 00:02:55,185
- SANGO CAN HANDLE HERSELF,

32
00:02:55,219 --> 00:02:57,385
SO I KNOW THAT
I SHOULDN'T BE WORRIED,

33
00:02:57,419 --> 00:02:59,152
BUT STILL...

34
00:03:04,552 --> 00:03:06,585
- [BIRDS CHIRPING]

35
00:03:06,619 --> 00:03:09,219
- [HAMMERING]

36
00:03:19,719 --> 00:03:22,352
[FIRE CRACKLING]

37
00:03:26,252 --> 00:03:28,819
- [GRUNTING]

38
00:03:52,319 --> 00:03:54,885
- [GRUNTING]

39
00:03:55,819 --> 00:03:58,352
[SIZZLING]

40
00:04:00,352 --> 00:04:01,319
- HUH.

41
00:04:01,352 --> 00:04:03,785
WELL, IT'S NOT AS GOOD
AS FATHER'S HANDIWORK WAS,

42
00:04:03,819 --> 00:04:07,952
BUT I HAVE TO ADMIT,
YOU KNOW, IT'S NOT BAD.

43
00:04:10,319 --> 00:04:11,185
AHH.

44
00:04:11,219 --> 00:04:13,885
- [BIRDS CHIRPING]

45
00:04:22,352 --> 00:04:25,385
- DEAR FATHER,
MY FAMILY, AND FRIENDS,

46
00:04:25,419 --> 00:04:27,085
WE'VE FINALLY COME HOME AT LAST.

47
00:04:27,119 --> 00:04:33,119
PLEASE FORGIVE ME FOR
TAKING SO LONG TO BRING
YOUR REMAINS BACK.

48
00:04:37,719 --> 00:04:39,152
UNH!

49
00:04:43,385 --> 00:04:46,919
- NOW, SANGO, DO YOU THINK
YOU CAN CONTINUE

50
00:04:46,952 --> 00:04:48,985
AS A DEMON SLAYER?

51
00:04:49,952 --> 00:04:50,785
- WHY, YES, FATHER.

52
00:04:50,819 --> 00:04:54,319
I BELIEVE I'M SUITED
TO THIS OCCUPATION.

53
00:04:54,352 --> 00:04:56,119
- I SEE.

54
00:04:59,052 --> 00:05:00,419
SANGO, I HAVE TRAINED YOU

55
00:05:00,452 --> 00:05:03,852
NOT MERELY SO YOU CAN
CONTINUE OUR TRADITION.

56
00:05:03,885 --> 00:05:07,885
I WANT YOU TO LIVE
A STRONG LIFE.

57
00:05:11,919 --> 00:05:17,719
- OH, FATHER, WHAT WAS IT
YOU WERE TRYING TO TELL ME?

58
00:05:21,152 --> 00:05:23,719
- [GROWLING]

59
00:05:25,085 --> 00:05:26,219
- HUH?

60
00:05:26,252 --> 00:05:27,685
UNH!

61
00:05:30,319 --> 00:05:32,885
- [SNARLING]

62
00:05:32,919 --> 00:05:35,452
[ROARING]

63
00:05:35,485 --> 00:05:36,385
- AAH!

64
00:05:36,419 --> 00:05:39,219
[MOANING]

65
00:05:39,252 --> 00:05:41,785
- [SNARLS]

66
00:05:42,952 --> 00:05:44,019
- PLEASE STOP!

67
00:05:44,052 --> 00:05:46,419
DON'T HURT HER! LET HER GO!

68
00:05:46,452 --> 00:05:47,919
- KILLALLA!

69
00:05:47,952 --> 00:05:50,519
- [GROWLING]

70
00:05:58,619 --> 00:06:02,285
- WHO ARE YOU,
AND WHAT DO YOU WANT HERE?

71
00:06:05,285 --> 00:06:06,152
- SISTER!

72
00:06:06,185 --> 00:06:07,119
- WHAT'S WRONG?

73
00:06:07,152 --> 00:06:10,419
- WE HAVEN'T HAD
FOOD OR WATER FOR 3 DAYS.

74
00:06:10,452 --> 00:06:13,152
- [STOMACH GROWLING]

75
00:06:18,719 --> 00:06:20,985
- MMM, MMM, MMM.

76
00:06:21,019 --> 00:06:23,219
- ISN'T THIS DELICIOUS, SERENA?

77
00:06:23,252 --> 00:06:25,419
- MM-HMM.

78
00:06:25,985 --> 00:06:29,152
- THERE'S MORE.
DO YOU WANT ANOTHER SERVING?

79
00:06:29,185 --> 00:06:30,352
- YES, PLEASE.

80
00:06:30,385 --> 00:06:31,852
- HUH?

81
00:06:31,885 --> 00:06:35,052
- UM, PARDON MY MANNERS.
I AM SERENA.

82
00:06:35,085 --> 00:06:38,219
- AND I'M HER SISTER,
SASUNA. HA HA!

83
00:06:38,252 --> 00:06:41,552
- THE TWO OF US RECENTLY SET OUT
FROM OUR VILLAGE FOLLOWING LEADS

84
00:06:41,585 --> 00:06:44,585
IN SEARCH OF THE DEMON SLAYERS'
HIDDEN VILLAGE.

85
00:06:44,619 --> 00:06:45,752
- SO YOU ATTACKED ME,

86
00:06:45,785 --> 00:06:48,485
DESPITE THE FACT THAT
YOU KNEW I WAS A SLAYER?

87
00:06:48,519 --> 00:06:50,719
- WE JUST WANTED
TO TEST YOUR SKILLS.

88
00:06:50,752 --> 00:06:53,185
YOU REALLY ARE QUITE GOOD, MISS.

89
00:06:53,219 --> 00:06:54,652
OH!

90
00:06:55,019 --> 00:06:58,452
- WILL YOU TAKE US ON
AS YOUR APPRENTICES?

91
00:06:58,485 --> 00:06:59,419
- APPRENTICES?

92
00:06:59,452 --> 00:07:02,219
- YOU LOOK LIKE
YOU COULD USE A GOOD RUBDOWN.

93
00:07:02,252 --> 00:07:02,885
HA HA HA!

94
00:07:02,919 --> 00:07:06,419
- TEACHER, PLEASE, ACCEPT US.

95
00:07:06,452 --> 00:07:07,119
- NO.

96
00:07:07,152 --> 00:07:09,585
- OH, COME ON, PLEASE, TEACHER?

97
00:07:09,619 --> 00:07:11,685
- I SAID NO.

98
00:07:12,319 --> 00:07:13,985
- PLEASE, TEACHER!

99
00:07:14,019 --> 00:07:17,785
- I AM NOT YOUR TEACHER,
AND NO MEANS NO.

100
00:07:17,819 --> 00:07:21,185
NOW, WOULD YOU LET ME GO?
I'M IN A HURRY!

101
00:07:22,252 --> 00:07:24,119
- WE CANNOT RETURN HOME
TO OUR VILLAGE

102
00:07:24,152 --> 00:07:25,919
UNTIL YOU TAKE US IN
AS YOUR PUPILS

103
00:07:25,952 --> 00:07:28,585
AND TRAIN US
IN THE ART OF DEMON SLAYING!

104
00:07:28,619 --> 00:07:30,152
- PLEASE!

105
00:07:32,652 --> 00:07:35,185
[WAILING]

106
00:07:36,085 --> 00:07:37,652
- [SIGH]

107
00:07:37,685 --> 00:07:39,985
I SUPPOSE I SHOULD HEAR YOU OUT.

108
00:07:40,452 --> 00:07:42,385
- YOU SEE,
MY SISTER SASUNA AND I

109
00:07:42,419 --> 00:07:46,052
LIVE IN A SMALL FARMING VILLAGE
HIGH UP IN THE MOUNTAINS.

110
00:07:46,085 --> 00:07:47,285
WE WANTED TO EXPAND THE FARM,

111
00:07:47,319 --> 00:07:48,919
SO WE STARTED
CLEARING THE MOUNTAIN

112
00:07:48,952 --> 00:07:50,319
BELONGING TO OUR LOCAL DEITY.

113
00:07:50,352 --> 00:07:52,852
THAT WAS WHEN THE DEMONS
BEGAN ATTACKING US.

114
00:07:52,885 --> 00:07:55,919
- LOTS OF THEM,
NOT JUST ONE OR TWO.

115
00:07:55,952 --> 00:07:59,719
- AND SADLY,
MANY OF THE VILLAGERS
HAVE BEEN SLAUGHTERED.

116
00:07:59,752 --> 00:08:02,219
THE ABLE-BODIED PEOPLE
HAVE MOVED TO ANOTHER VILLAGE.

117
00:08:02,252 --> 00:08:04,819
BUT THE ELDERLY AND THOSE
WITH CHILDREN CANNOT LEAVE,

118
00:08:04,852 --> 00:08:09,319
AND THEY SPEND EVERY
WAKING MOMENT LIVING IN TERROR.

119
00:08:09,352 --> 00:08:10,352
- I SEE.

120
00:08:10,385 --> 00:08:13,285
THE DEITY'S FOREST HAD ACTED
AS A BARRIER FOR YOU.

121
00:08:13,319 --> 00:08:15,019
- YES, AND IT WAS
ABOUT THAT TIME

122
00:08:15,052 --> 00:08:18,185
THAT WE HEARD OF A VILLAGE
OF DEMON SLAYERS.

123
00:08:18,219 --> 00:08:19,352
- AS YOU CAN SEE,

124
00:08:19,385 --> 00:08:22,719
THERE ARE NO SLAYERS
LEFT IN THIS VILLAGE.

125
00:08:22,752 --> 00:08:25,352
- OHH.

126
00:08:25,385 --> 00:08:26,485
- HMM.

127
00:08:26,519 --> 00:08:29,052
- MAYBE I COULD GO BACK TO
YOUR VILLAGE WITH YOU TO HELP.

128
00:08:29,085 --> 00:08:32,719
- BUT OUR VILLAGE DOESN'T
HAVE ANY MONEY TO PAY YOU.

129
00:08:32,752 --> 00:08:34,552
WE HAVE COME ONLY TO LEARN.

130
00:08:34,585 --> 00:08:36,019
WE HAD NO INTENTION WHATSOEVER

131
00:08:36,052 --> 00:08:39,319
OF HIRING A DEMON SLAYER
TO BRING BACK HOME WITH US.

132
00:08:39,352 --> 00:08:42,485
- BESIDES,
OUR VILLAGE IS FAR AWAY.

133
00:08:42,519 --> 00:08:45,419
- EVEN IF WE DID STAVE THEM OFF
ONCE OR TWICE,

134
00:08:45,452 --> 00:08:46,552
THOSE DEMONS WOULD RETURN,

135
00:08:46,585 --> 00:08:49,519
SO PLEASE TEACH US
TO DEFEND OURSELVES.

136
00:08:49,552 --> 00:08:52,652
WE WILL TRAIN HARD
FOR OUR PEOPLE.

137
00:08:53,252 --> 00:08:54,319
- SASUNA.

138
00:08:54,352 --> 00:08:56,385
- I'LL DO MY BEST.

139
00:08:56,419 --> 00:08:58,185
- YOU MUST UNDERSTAND,

140
00:08:58,219 --> 00:09:01,585
THE ART OF DEMON SLAYING ISN'T
SOMETHING ONE LEARNS OVERNIGHT.

141
00:09:01,619 --> 00:09:07,052
I SUPPOSE I COULD TEACH YOU HOW
TO DETER LESSER DEMONS, THOUGH.

142
00:09:07,085 --> 00:09:08,185
- OH!

143
00:09:08,219 --> 00:09:09,519
- THANK YOU!

144
00:09:09,552 --> 00:09:12,119
- MIROKU AND THE OTHERS
WILL WAIT FOR ME,

145
00:09:12,152 --> 00:09:15,619
EVEN IF I COME BACK
ONE OR TWO DAYS LATE.

146
00:09:21,819 --> 00:09:25,885
THESE ARE THE WEAPONS
YOU'LL USE TO WARD OFF DEMONS.

147
00:09:25,919 --> 00:09:27,419
- RIGHT!

148
00:09:29,019 --> 00:09:30,252
HMM?

149
00:09:30,285 --> 00:09:31,985
UH...

150
00:09:36,152 --> 00:09:37,619
- HMM.

151
00:09:39,585 --> 00:09:43,119
- THIS IS AS GOOD A PLACE
AS ANY TO START.

152
00:09:48,019 --> 00:09:51,285
DON'T JUST STAND THERE,
HELP ME FAN.

153
00:09:59,252 --> 00:10:01,185
- [COUGHING]

154
00:10:01,219 --> 00:10:02,619
WHAT IS THIS?

155
00:10:02,652 --> 00:10:06,819
- A POWDERED MIXTURE OF HERBS
AND REMEDIES THAT DEMONS DETEST.

156
00:10:06,852 --> 00:10:09,452
- SO THIS WOULD SLAY A DEMON?

157
00:10:09,485 --> 00:10:12,385
- IT WOULD BE ENOUGH
TO PROTECT THE VILLAGE.

158
00:10:12,419 --> 00:10:14,719
- [SQUAWKING]

159
00:10:14,752 --> 00:10:17,319
- [COUGHING]

160
00:10:18,819 --> 00:10:20,052
- THIS SMOKE IS INCREDIBLE!

161
00:10:20,085 --> 00:10:23,352
ARE YOU SURE IT WILL WARD OFF
THE DEMONS, THOUGH?

162
00:10:23,385 --> 00:10:25,952
- [COUGHING]

163
00:10:26,752 --> 00:10:28,885
- UM, SISTER--I MEAN, TEACHER,

164
00:10:28,919 --> 00:10:32,452
ISN'T THERE A MORE EXCITING
TECHNIQUE THAT YOU CAN SHOW US?

165
00:10:32,485 --> 00:10:35,419
- LEARNING TECHNIQUES
WITHOUT FULLY UNDERSTANDING THEM

166
00:10:35,452 --> 00:10:36,685
CAN BE DANGEROUS.

167
00:10:36,719 --> 00:10:37,852
THE DAY IS ALMOST OVER,

168
00:10:37,885 --> 00:10:41,652
SO I'LL SHOW BOTH OF YOU HOW
TO MAKE THIS POWDER TOMORROW.

169
00:10:41,685 --> 00:10:43,919
- HMM.

170
00:10:43,952 --> 00:10:48,052
- SANGO STILL HASN'T COME BACK.

171
00:10:50,419 --> 00:10:51,352
HMM?

172
00:10:51,385 --> 00:10:54,119
- UM, I'D LIKE TO ASK YOU
A QUESTION, KAGOME.

173
00:10:54,152 --> 00:10:55,119
- YEAH?

174
00:10:55,152 --> 00:10:57,585
- DO YOU BELIEVE THAT
STROKING A WOMAN'S BOTTOM

175
00:10:57,619 --> 00:11:01,985
COULD DESTROY THE MUTUAL TRUST
BETWEEN TWO PEOPLE?

176
00:11:03,485 --> 00:11:04,585
- FIRST OF ALL,

177
00:11:04,619 --> 00:11:07,585
TRUST IS BUILT BY RESPECTING
EACH OTHER'S PERSONAL SPACE.

178
00:11:07,619 --> 00:11:09,885
- IS THAT REALLY HOW IT IS?

179
00:11:09,919 --> 00:11:10,885
- IF SANGO DOESN'T COME BACK,

180
00:11:10,919 --> 00:11:13,319
IT'S YOU I'M GOING TO BE
POINTING THE FINGER AT.

181
00:11:13,352 --> 00:11:15,952
- SHE'LL COME BACK, ALL RIGHT.

182
00:11:15,985 --> 00:11:18,619
[METAL JINGLING]

183
00:11:20,185 --> 00:11:24,752
- HE SOUNDS CONFIDENT,
BUT HE SURE DOESN'T LOOK IT.

184
00:11:24,785 --> 00:11:26,619
- HUMPH!

185
00:11:46,085 --> 00:11:49,119
- SERENA, LET ME DO IT!

186
00:11:51,385 --> 00:11:52,519
HAH!

187
00:11:52,552 --> 00:11:54,585
THAT WAS EASY ENOUGH
TO BREAK OFF.

188
00:11:54,619 --> 00:11:56,819
CAN'T BEAT A NINJA'S SKILLS! HA!

189
00:11:56,852 --> 00:12:00,252
- THANKS. I COULDN'T
HAVE DONE IT WITHOUT YOU.

190
00:12:04,752 --> 00:12:05,619
- LOOK AT ALL THIS!

191
00:12:05,652 --> 00:12:08,252
- THIS IS EXACTLY
LIKE OUR FATHER TOLD US.

192
00:12:08,285 --> 00:12:12,685
THESE MATERIALS ARE THE SECRET
TO THE SLAYER'S WEAPONS.

193
00:12:12,719 --> 00:12:13,519
- THESE THINGS?

194
00:12:13,552 --> 00:12:16,719
- THE FANGS, BONES,
HIDES OF DEMONS.

195
00:12:16,752 --> 00:12:19,752
- NO WONDER SLAYERS CAN
WARD OFF THEIR ATTACKS.

196
00:12:19,785 --> 00:12:21,852
- THEN WE CAN
BECOME JUST AS STRONG

197
00:12:21,885 --> 00:12:23,419
IF WE TAKE THESE MATERIALS.

198
00:12:23,452 --> 00:12:26,652
- WE'LL BE ALMOST INVINCIBLE.

199
00:12:29,619 --> 00:12:31,352
- [GASPS]

200
00:12:31,385 --> 00:12:33,152
- WHAT DID YOU STOP FOR?

201
00:12:33,185 --> 00:12:35,552
- WHAT ARE YOU TWO UP TO?

202
00:12:35,585 --> 00:12:36,819
I WANT THE TRUTH!

203
00:12:36,852 --> 00:12:40,019
YOU'RE NO ORDINARY
VILLAGE GIRLS.

204
00:12:40,552 --> 00:12:42,452
- HAH!
- UNH!

205
00:12:42,485 --> 00:12:43,952
- HAH!

206
00:12:45,485 --> 00:12:46,919
- HAH!

207
00:12:46,952 --> 00:12:49,219
- THOSE MOVES.

208
00:12:49,252 --> 00:12:55,019
- CORRECT. BOTH MY SISTER AND I
COME FROM A VILLAGE OF NINJAS.

209
00:12:55,752 --> 00:12:58,185
- [ROARING]

210
00:12:58,219 --> 00:13:01,919
- ONE DAY THE CLAN LORDS
DEMANDED THAT WE SLAY A DEMON,

211
00:13:01,952 --> 00:13:04,785
SOMETHING WE HAD
NEVER DONE BEFORE.

212
00:13:05,752 --> 00:13:11,019
- WE WERE ABLE TO USE OUR NINJA
SKILLS TO DESTROY THE ONE DEMON.

213
00:13:11,619 --> 00:13:13,785
BUT OTHERS CAME SEEKING REVENGE.

214
00:13:13,819 --> 00:13:16,019
OUR PEOPLE KNEW
ONLY NINJA TACTICS,

215
00:13:16,052 --> 00:13:19,285
AND NEARLY ALL WERE DEVOURED
BY THESE DEMONS.

216
00:13:19,319 --> 00:13:21,919
- [SCREAMING]

217
00:13:37,452 --> 00:13:41,519
- SERENA, I THINK IT'S SAFE
FOR US TO COME OUT NOW.

218
00:13:47,585 --> 00:13:48,619
- FATHER!

219
00:13:48,652 --> 00:13:49,819
- FATHER, NO!

220
00:13:49,852 --> 00:13:52,185
FATHER, HOLD ON.

221
00:13:53,185 --> 00:13:54,819
- [MOANING]

222
00:13:54,852 --> 00:14:00,352
- SERENA, SASUNA,
YOU NEED TO BE STRONG FOR ME,

223
00:14:00,385 --> 00:14:01,719
BOTH OF YOU.

224
00:14:01,752 --> 00:14:04,152
[GROAN]

225
00:14:04,185 --> 00:14:05,252
- FATHER!

226
00:14:05,285 --> 00:14:07,085
- FATHER!

227
00:14:07,285 --> 00:14:10,085
- THOSE WERE OUR FATHER'S
DYING WORDS TO US.

228
00:14:10,119 --> 00:14:11,385
- "BE STRONG."

229
00:14:11,419 --> 00:14:14,819
HE MUST HAVE WANTED US
TO RESTORE OUR VILLAGE
TO ITS FORMER GLORY.

230
00:14:14,852 --> 00:14:18,619
I'M CERTAIN THAT'S
WHAT HE WAS TRYING TO TELL US.

231
00:14:18,652 --> 00:14:19,785
- HMM.

232
00:14:19,819 --> 00:14:21,485
- HOLD ON.

233
00:14:21,519 --> 00:14:23,852
- DO IT NOW, SERENA.

234
00:14:24,719 --> 00:14:26,185
- AH!

235
00:14:26,619 --> 00:14:29,185
- [COUGHING]

236
00:14:34,885 --> 00:14:36,285
- OH, NO.

237
00:14:36,319 --> 00:14:40,419
SOME OF THOSE REMAINS
HAVEN'T BEEN EXORCISED
OF THE DEMON SPIRITS YET,

238
00:14:40,452 --> 00:14:44,352
MEANING THEY'LL SUMMON
OTHER DEMONS BACK HERE!

239
00:14:44,385 --> 00:14:46,085
KILLALLA!

240
00:14:53,919 --> 00:14:55,085
HURRY, KILLALLA.

241
00:14:55,119 --> 00:14:57,485
THOSE GIRLS ARE IN DANGER!

242
00:15:00,952 --> 00:15:02,685
- [PANTING]

243
00:15:02,719 --> 00:15:04,385
- WAIT FOR ME, SASUNA.

244
00:15:04,419 --> 00:15:06,952
- HURRY UP!
YOU'RE ALWAYS SLOWING ME DOWN.

245
00:15:06,985 --> 00:15:09,385
I'LL TAKE SOME
OF YOUR LOAD FOR YOU.

246
00:15:09,419 --> 00:15:11,519
- [HEAVY BREATHING]

247
00:15:11,552 --> 00:15:12,452
- I'M SORRY.

248
00:15:12,485 --> 00:15:15,219
- NO WONDER FATHER SETTLED
ON ME AS HIS HEIR,

249
00:15:15,252 --> 00:15:18,252
EVEN THOUGH YOU'RE THE ELDEST.

250
00:15:18,285 --> 00:15:19,785
- FORGIVE ME.

251
00:15:19,819 --> 00:15:20,652
I'LL TRAIN HARD,

252
00:15:20,685 --> 00:15:22,552
AND ONE DAY I WILL
BECOME A STRONG NINJA

253
00:15:22,585 --> 00:15:25,952
EXACTLY LIKE FATHER
WANTED ME TO BE.

254
00:15:27,352 --> 00:15:28,285
- HMM?

255
00:15:28,319 --> 00:15:30,819
- [GASP]

256
00:15:31,085 --> 00:15:33,185
- COME ON, LET'S HURRY.

257
00:15:37,085 --> 00:15:39,652
- [PANTING]

258
00:15:42,952 --> 00:15:43,885
- OH, NO!

259
00:15:43,919 --> 00:15:45,152
WHAT'S THAT?

260
00:15:45,185 --> 00:15:47,452
- [SNARL]

261
00:15:47,485 --> 00:15:49,485
[HISSING]
- AAH!

262
00:15:49,519 --> 00:15:51,585
- BOTH OF YOU,
GET ON KILLALLA NOW!

263
00:15:51,619 --> 00:15:53,185
WE'RE GOING BACK TO THE VILLAGE.

264
00:15:53,219 --> 00:15:55,019
- WE'RE NOT RETURNING THESE.

265
00:15:55,052 --> 00:15:56,985
- YOU MUST DISCARD THEM AT ONCE!

266
00:15:57,019 --> 00:15:58,119
HUNDREDS OF DEMONS ARE COMING

267
00:15:58,152 --> 00:16:01,819
IN SEARCH OF THE DEMONIC AURA
THOSE WEAPONS ARE EXUDING.

268
00:16:01,852 --> 00:16:02,485
- HUH?

269
00:16:02,519 --> 00:16:05,119
- IT'S THE TRUTH. NOW, HURRY!

270
00:16:16,885 --> 00:16:19,452
- [GROWLING]

271
00:16:25,185 --> 00:16:27,952
- WE'RE TOO LATE.

272
00:16:35,958 --> 00:16:38,524
- [GROWLING]

273
00:16:39,662 --> 00:16:41,796
- WE'RE TOO LATE.

274
00:16:44,229 --> 00:16:46,229
I'LL HAVE TO DESTROY
THOSE DEMONS,

275
00:16:46,262 --> 00:16:47,329
THEN WE'LL ESCAPE.

276
00:16:47,362 --> 00:16:48,529
- SISTER, BE STRONG.

277
00:16:48,562 --> 00:16:51,996
THE TIME HAS FINALLY COME FOR US
TO SHOW FATHER OUR COURAGE.

278
00:16:52,029 --> 00:16:54,262
- WE'LL DO OUR NINJA
ANCESTORS PROUD.

279
00:16:54,296 --> 00:16:59,196
WE HAVE A CHANCE AS LONG
AS WE HAVE THESE WEAPONS.

280
00:17:00,596 --> 00:17:06,229
- SERENA, SASUNA,
YOU NEED TO BE STRONG FOR ME,

281
00:17:06,262 --> 00:17:07,596
BOTH OF YOU.

282
00:17:07,629 --> 00:17:08,896
[GROAN]

283
00:17:08,929 --> 00:17:13,129
- I TRAINED YOU
NOT MERELY SO YOU COULD
CONTINUE OUR TRADITION.

284
00:17:13,162 --> 00:17:16,762
I WANT YOU TO LIVE STRONG.

285
00:17:16,796 --> 00:17:18,062
- OH, FATHER.

286
00:17:18,096 --> 00:17:19,296
- HA!
- HAH!

287
00:17:19,329 --> 00:17:21,996
- WAIT! YOU'RE MISTAKEN!

288
00:17:22,029 --> 00:17:22,996
- HUH?

289
00:17:23,029 --> 00:17:25,562
- THIS IS NOT HOW YOUR FATHER
WANTED YOU TO BE.

290
00:17:25,596 --> 00:17:28,196
YOU HAVE TO BELIEVE ME, PLEASE!

291
00:17:28,229 --> 00:17:28,896
- HUH?

292
00:17:28,929 --> 00:17:30,229
- WHAT WOULD YOU KNOW ABOUT HIM?

293
00:17:30,262 --> 00:17:31,596
- THERE ISN'T A FATHER
IN THE WORLD

294
00:17:31,629 --> 00:17:34,962
THAT DOESN'T WISH
FOR HIS DAUGHTER'S HAPPINESS.

295
00:17:35,562 --> 00:17:39,462
YOUR FATHER WASN'T TELLING YOU
TO CONTINUE THE NINJA TRADITION.

296
00:17:39,496 --> 00:17:41,529
HE WANTED YOU
TO BE STRONG INSIDE.

297
00:17:41,562 --> 00:17:46,562
HE WANTED YOU TO BE HAPPY.
THAT'S WHAT HE REALLY MEANT.

298
00:17:46,596 --> 00:17:48,696
- WHAT DO YOU THINK?

299
00:17:50,096 --> 00:17:52,029
- NOW CLIMB ON TOP OF KILLALLA,

300
00:17:52,062 --> 00:17:54,962
AND MAKE SURE
YOU STAY CLOSE TO ME.

301
00:17:54,996 --> 00:17:57,562
- [GROWLING]

302
00:18:03,596 --> 00:18:08,529
- BE STRONG FOR ME, BOTH OF YOU.

303
00:18:08,562 --> 00:18:12,062
- HE WANTED YOU
TO BE STRONG INSIDE.

304
00:18:12,096 --> 00:18:15,529
HE WANTED YOU TO BE HAPPY.

305
00:18:19,696 --> 00:18:21,829
- [DEMONS GROWLING]

306
00:18:21,862 --> 00:18:23,529
- SASUNA!

307
00:18:23,562 --> 00:18:26,929
- HUH? WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

308
00:18:26,962 --> 00:18:27,662
AAH!

309
00:18:27,696 --> 00:18:31,329
- SANGO'S RIGHT, I'M SURE OF IT.

310
00:18:31,362 --> 00:18:32,962
- UNH!

311
00:18:32,996 --> 00:18:34,496
- SANGO!

312
00:18:36,329 --> 00:18:38,896
- [GROWLING]

313
00:18:39,462 --> 00:18:41,896
- HIRAIKOTSU!

314
00:18:47,462 --> 00:18:49,396
- LET'S GO!

315
00:18:53,162 --> 00:18:55,562
STAY OUT OF MY WAY!

316
00:18:56,396 --> 00:18:58,396
- [ROARS]

317
00:18:58,429 --> 00:19:00,096
- HYAH!

318
00:19:00,129 --> 00:19:02,696
- [GROWLING]

319
00:19:09,229 --> 00:19:11,796
- [GRUNTING]

320
00:19:17,129 --> 00:19:18,729
- AAH!
- OH!

321
00:19:18,762 --> 00:19:21,029
- [GROWLING]
- AAH!

322
00:19:21,062 --> 00:19:22,396
- SASUNA!

323
00:19:22,429 --> 00:19:24,962
- TAKE THAT!

324
00:19:24,996 --> 00:19:26,062
AAH!

325
00:19:26,096 --> 00:19:27,329
UNH!

326
00:19:27,362 --> 00:19:29,162
- SASUNA!

327
00:19:32,696 --> 00:19:33,496
SASUNA?

328
00:19:33,529 --> 00:19:35,329
- [WEAKLY] SERENA.

329
00:19:40,229 --> 00:19:42,396
- STAY BACK!

330
00:19:42,429 --> 00:19:44,996
- [GRUNTING]

331
00:19:45,429 --> 00:19:47,996
- [SNARLING]

332
00:19:48,662 --> 00:19:51,229
- [GROWLING]

333
00:20:02,096 --> 00:20:04,196
[METAL JINGLES]

334
00:20:04,229 --> 00:20:05,729
- SANGO!

335
00:20:06,162 --> 00:20:08,762
- [GRUNTING]

336
00:20:08,796 --> 00:20:10,329
- MIROKU!

337
00:20:11,829 --> 00:20:14,329
- WIND SCAR!

338
00:20:24,296 --> 00:20:25,362
- HEY, SANGO, IT'S NOT LIKE YOU

339
00:20:25,396 --> 00:20:28,729
TO HAVE YOUR DEPARTURE DELAYED
BY THE LIKES OF DEMONS.

340
00:20:28,762 --> 00:20:29,996
- INUYASHA.

341
00:20:30,029 --> 00:20:32,329
- I'LL TAKE OVER NOW.

342
00:20:33,596 --> 00:20:35,462
- WIND TUNNEL!

343
00:20:54,196 --> 00:20:55,662
- HI, SANGO!

344
00:20:55,696 --> 00:20:57,962
- WE CAME BACK TO GET YOU.

345
00:20:57,996 --> 00:21:00,262
- THANK YOU.

346
00:21:17,096 --> 00:21:19,196
- LET'S BE ON OUR WAY, SISTER.

347
00:21:19,229 --> 00:21:20,696
- HMM.

348
00:21:27,729 --> 00:21:31,096
- BE STRONG, BOTH OF YOU.

349
00:21:31,129 --> 00:21:34,596
- WELL, MIROKU WAS WORRIED,
SO WE DECIDED TO COME.

350
00:21:34,629 --> 00:21:36,529
IT'S A GOOD THING WE DID, TOO.

351
00:21:36,562 --> 00:21:40,296
- WELL, I'M GLAD
WE MADE IT ON TIME.

352
00:21:44,362 --> 00:21:49,396
- MIROKU, WERE YOU ACTUALLY
THAT WORRIED ABOUT ME?

353
00:21:49,429 --> 00:21:51,896
- OH, CALL IT A PREMONITION,
IF YOU WILL.

354
00:21:51,929 --> 00:21:55,029
I KEPT SEEING YOUR FACE, SANGO,
NO MATTER WHAT I DID.

355
00:21:55,062 --> 00:21:57,862
I SIMPLY COULDN'T
GET YOU OUT OF MY MIND.

356
00:21:57,896 --> 00:22:00,096
IT'S THE TRUTH.

357
00:22:02,496 --> 00:22:04,162
- [SLAP]

358
00:22:04,196 --> 00:22:07,429
- THANK YOU FOR YOUR CONCERN.

359
00:22:07,462 --> 00:22:09,096
- DON'T MENTION IT. HA HA HA!

360
00:22:09,129 --> 00:22:12,062
- WHEN IS HE EVER GONNA LEARN?

361
00:22:12,096 --> 00:22:15,862
PLEASE DON'T LET ME GROW UP
TO BE LIKE HIM.

362
00:22:15,896 --> 00:22:16,962
- MM-HMM.

363
00:22:31,201 --> 00:22:33,934
[SINGING IN JAPANESE]

364
00:23:58,667 --> 00:24:01,167
- KAGOME, NARAKU'S BROUGHT IN
AN EVIL PRIESTESS

365
00:24:01,201 --> 00:24:02,834
THAT FOUGHT WITH KIKYO
A LONG TIME AGO.

366
00:24:02,867 --> 00:24:06,267
- OH, NO! I CAN'T FIGURE IT OUT!
I CAN'T FOLLOW THE LESSONS!

367
00:24:06,301 --> 00:24:09,067
- SHE'S USING THE SACRED JEWEL
TO CAST A SPELL ON YOU.

368
00:24:09,101 --> 00:24:13,034
- EVERYONE KEEPS TELLING ME
TO BREAK UP WITH INUYASHA, TOO.

369
00:24:13,067 --> 00:24:14,201
- WOULD YOU LISTEN TO ME?

370
00:24:14,234 --> 00:24:15,167
- DO YOU KNOW
WHAT THEY CALL YOU?

371
00:24:15,201 --> 00:24:18,134
MY VIOLENT, POSSESSIVE,
TWO-TIMING BOYFRIEND!

372
00:24:18,167 --> 00:24:19,734
- WHY? WHAT DID I EVER DO?

373
00:24:19,767 --> 00:24:23,667
- NEXT TIME...

374
00:24:23,701 --> 00:24:24,934
RUN, INUYASHA!

375
00:24:24,967 --> 00:24:25,967
- TWO-TIMING?!

